---
import { resolvePath } from "../../utils/paths";
const bgImage = resolvePath("/images/jeweler-appraising.webp");
---

<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div
        class="relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-[#d4af37]/30 bg-[#111111]"
    >
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
            {/* Image Side */}
            <div class="h-[300px] lg:h-auto min-h-[400px] relative">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center filter grayscale-[20%]"
                    style={`background-image: url('${bgImage}');`}
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/80 to-transparent lg:hidden"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-l from-[#111111] via-transparent to-transparent hidden lg:block"
                >
                </div>
            </div>

            {/* Content Side */}
            <div
                class="p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-20 flex flex-col justify-center text-left"
            >
                <span
                    class="text-[#d4af37] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4"
                    >Servicio Exclusivo en Miami</span
                >

                <h2
                    class="text-[#FAFAF5] font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-6 leading-tight"
                >
                    ¿Tienes oro que ya <br />
                    <span class="text-[#d4af37] italic">no usas?</span>
                </h2>

                <p
                    class="text-gray-300 text-lg font-light mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-md"
                >
                    En DTalles compramos tu oro al mejor precio de mercado en
                    Miami. Tasación transparente frente a ti, segura y al
                    instante. También ofrecemos el "Plan Renueva": usa tu oro
                    viejo como parte de pago (+20% valor).
                </p>

                <div
                    class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 items-start sm:items-center"
                >
                    <a
                        href="/vender-oro"
                        class="bg-black text-[#d4af37] border border-[#d4af37] px-8 py-4 font-bold tracking-widest text-xs uppercase hover:bg-[#d4af37] hover:text-black transition-all"
                    >
                        Cotizar Mi Oro
                    </a>

                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#d4af37]"
                            >location_on</span
                        >
                        <span>123 Seybold Building, Miami, FL</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
